title: Rescue of stranded astronauts is a win for Musk. This fund offers a ride on the SpaceX roller coaster.
body: When the SpaceX Crew Dragon capsule carrying NASA astronauts Butch Wilmore and Suni Williams splashed down in the Gulf of Mexico off the coast of Florida on Tuesday, it ended a nine-month saga that began as what was supposed to be an eight-day stint on the International Space Station.

title: SpaceX to take humans to Mars in next 20-30 years? Elon Musk claims it's possible
body: Elon Musk predicts humans will travel to Mars in 20-30 years, emphasising SpaceX's goal to take anyone interested. Starship, the largest rocket, is crucial for this vision and is expected to launch by the end of 2026,
